== Merchandise Lab ==
VRChat's current official outlet for merchandise is hosted on their "Merch Lab". It was launched<ref>[https://ask.vrchat.com/t/developer-update-30-may-2024/24821 'Developer Update - 30 May 2024'] on ''ask.vrchat.com''; retrieved November 27, 2024.</ref> on May 30, 2024, and includes an assortment of clothing and accessories. These products are also known as "VRChat Gear", stylized as ''VRCGEAR.''